	<section id="ValidationHelper_Methods3">
	<title>SetSubmitOptions(Boolean confirm, Boolean disable, Boolean groupError, Int32 errorMode) 
</title>

<p>
 Configure the submit and validation options. 
</p>



	<p>
	<table class="commontable">
	<tr>
		<th>Parameter</th>
		<th>Description</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><tt>confirm</tt></td>
		<td>
<b>True</b> for submit confirmation. Otherwise, <b>false</b>.
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><tt>disable</tt></td>
		<td>
<b>True</b> for submit buttons disabling.
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><tt>groupError</tt></td>
		<td>
<b>True</b> for error grouping.
		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><tt>errorMode</tt></td>
		<td>
<tt>System.Int32</tt> representing the error mode.
		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	</p>
